{"word":"μοιράω","slug":"μοιράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μοιράω</b></el> <el>(μοιράω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μοῖρα'><el>μοῖρα</el></a>\n<p/><i>to share, divide, distribute</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>; <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to divide among themselves</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be allotted</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}